## Detection Rule: VPN Brute Force

### Query
Syslog
| where SyslogMessage contains "%ASA-6-113015"
| summarize FailedAttempts=count() by SrcIP, bin(TimeGenerated, 5m)
| where FailedAttempts > 100

### Logic
Trigger alert when:
- >100 failures
- Within 5 minutes
- Same source IP

### Severity
Medium / High

### MITRE
T1110 - Brute Force

### False Positives
- Internal scanners
- Security testing tools
